PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Product Discovery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the app find new products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms and data mining techniques to scour the internet for the latest product releases across various categories. We analyze social media trends, reviews, and sales data to identify hot new items.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of products can I discover?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app covers a wide range of product categories including electronics, fashion, home goods, beauty, and more. We aim to surface unique and innovative products from both big brands and small makers.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often is the app updated with new products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We continually update our database in real-time as new products hit the market. Our users always have access to the freshest and trendiest product discoveries.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I filter or customize my product feed?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! You can set preferences for product categories, price ranges, brands, and other criteria to personalize the new products displayed just for your interests.
